data.description: A family home in Manitowish Waters is a special place & this home is a hidden treasure. This large 3-bedroom home has an office, living room w/ fireplace, HUGE rec room that has a wall of windows & door to large south facing deck overlooking greenery of a cranberry farm.The updated kitchen has more storage than you could need w/ a generous sized island. The dining room is just off the kitchen. Enjoy the sunrise and sunsets in the huge screened in porch. Upper Level has a view of Little Trout Lake. Loon calls sing you to sleep and wildlife is seen from the front deck. Master suite is sweet with a wall of southern facing windows, full bath, two walk-in closets, and attached parlor/nursery-the entire 3rd floor! Room for everyone & everything, storage rooms,workshop,2 heated 1-car garages, garden area & cellar for canning or storage,& chicken coop. All just minutes from the Wild Rice boat landing for easy quick access to Manitowish Waters Chain. This is a family home to be cherished.
